## Medical Disclaimer

This software is for educational and research purposes only. It is not intended 
for use in medical diagnosis or treatment. Any medical decisions should always 
be made in consultation with qualified healthcare professionals. The authors 
and contributors of this software are not responsible for any medical decisions 
or outcomes resulting from the use of this software.

## Data Privacy Notice

This software is designed to handle medical imaging data. Users are responsible 
for ensuring compliance with all applicable data protection regulations, 
including but not limited to HIPAA, GDPR, and local privacy laws. The software 
does not automatically ensure compliance with these regulations.

